read) when not using <literal>AllowConcurrentRead</literal> property (which
bypasses row locking) for <classname>EmpressDictionary</classname>.
                    </para>
                </listitem>
                <listitem>
                    <para>
Only the category 2 non-local driver is supported.
                    </para>
                </listitem>
            </itemizedlist>
        </section>
    </section>
